<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zie khawvel lungkhamna cheng cheng,
 Pelin kumsawt nawpna gamah,
 A hehpihna thanuoi limah,
 Ka ngaih Lalpa'n ei dawn ding.

[V2]
 Um ta puona kikhenna leh,
 Lungkham buoina mitthi luonna;
 Ei Hukdampa Lal Isu chun,
 &quot;Hun thiek hulsak ka&quot; A tii.

[V3]
 2. Hukdampa chun mun a bawltai,
 Nawpna khawpi vak leh hawih chu;
 Zie lawpna mun lopi achun,
 Kumsawt in cheng den taitiu.

[V4]
 3. Kipakin van Angel vam tawh,
 Hukdam chate kikhawm hitiu;
 Kum khawsawt hinna changin,
 Kikhenna lau ta puoi tiu.

[V5]
 4. En leu hing Kalvari tangah,
 A lang ie I chenna ding gam;
 &quot;Van Belam No a leng&quot; a tiu,
 Gam vak hawih lopi achun.

[V6]
 5. Hukdampa hehpihna zieka,
 Kei le A lopina changin;
 Ziegam vak nuom chu ka tun tieng,
 Aw chawian lo thei puong ka.</lyrics>
<title>Angel Vam Te Tawh!</title>
<hymn_number>177</hymn_number>
<author>Kamlala</author>
</song>